15 March 2017The African National Congress sends its well wishes to Isithwalandwe/ Seaparankoe Cde Ahmed Kathrada who is in hospital following surgery. We wish Uncle Kathy a speedy recovery and further urge South Africans to continue their outpouring of support and thoughtful prayers for Cde Kathrada and his family during this time.Issued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National SpokespersonKhusela Sangoni 072 854 5707 National Communications Manager